                           <locus target="#00">Fols.
                                 2ra-b, 4vb: Mälkǝˁ-hymn
                                 in praise of the Trinity.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 2ra, ls.1-3: ሰላም፡ለህላዌክሙ፡ዘኢይመውዕ፡ለዊተ፡ለረከበ፡ስሙ፡ኅቡዕ፡ድኅረ፡ወጠንኩ፡ተምኔተ፡…</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#00" n="#">Fol. 5r (in the upper
                                 margin): Donation note.</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 5r: ዝመጽሐፍ፡
                                    ዘአቶ፡ ተንሥአ፡
                                    ክርስቶስ፡
                                    ዘተሣየጣ፡
                                    በወርቁ፡
                                    ዘወሀባ፡
                                    ለመቅደሰ፡
                                    ፈቃዳ፡ ወለቄሰ፡
                                    ገበዝሂ፡
                                    ጴጥሮስ፡ ኅቡረ፡
                                    ይምሐሮሙ፡
                                    {ዘሠረቃ፡
                                    ወዘፈሐቃ፡
                                    ውጉዘ፡
                                    ለይኩን።}</q>
                           <q xml:lang="en">Fol. 5r: This is a book of ˀato
                                    Tänśǝˀa
                                    Krǝstos, who bought it with his own money, who donated it
                                    to the sanctuary of Fäqada and to qesä gäbäz
                                    Ṗeṭros. May (God) be merciful to them both. He who
                                    steals it or erases (its text) shall be
                                 excommunicated.</q>
                           <p part="N"/>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus target="#00">Fols. 110ra-111vb: Prayer
                                 to the Virgin Mary for protection, unidentified, incomplete
                                 (?).</locus>
                           <q xml:lang="gez">Fol. 110ra, ls.11-14: ዘኢገብሮ፡እደ፡ሰብእ፡ዘሂ፡አስተዮ፡ለጽሙዕ፡በእንተ፡ስምኪ፡አስተዮ፡ጽዋዓ፡ሕይወት፡እምፈለገ፡
                              ማየ፡ሕይወት፡...</q>
